ple-watch-rift-but-it-takes-two-to-tango">he hasn’t heard from Apple</a> about potentially licensing the company’s blood oxygen tech. However, this is the first time we’ve seen Cook officially confirming it. </p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/02/01/apple-wont-license-masimos-patents-despite-apple-watch-import-ban#:~:text=Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20told,appeal%2C%22%20Cook&#x27;s%20statement%20said." rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Apple won&#x27;t license Masimo&#x27;s patents despite Apple Watch import ban</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->AppleInsider<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></li><li role="article" class="mx-[-16px] mb-40 mt-[-40px] px-16 last:mb-0 md:mx-0 md:px-0" id="stream-entry-072ed671-2919-4ffe-85df-8db83430d78d"><div class="border-solid border-blurple-df pt-40 sm:border-b-0 border-b"><div class="mb-40"><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card z-10 flex max-w-container-md flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col"><div class="mb-10 flex items-center"><div class="absolute left-[-2px] hidden h-6 w-12 border-y-2 border-white bg-[#DFCFFF] md:block"></div><div class="relative mr-8 block h-[36px] w-[36px] flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-solid border-gray-ef bg-[#DFCFFF]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="Wes Davis" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" da