/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 750w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/828x552/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 828w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/1080x720/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 1080w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/1200x800/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 1200w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/1440x960/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 1440w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/1920x1280/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 1920w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/2048x1365/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 2048w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/2400x1600/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg 2400w" src="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/2400x1600/filters:focal(656x533:657x534):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933442/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.jpg"/></noscript></span><div class="duet--media--caption pt-6 font-polysans-mono text-12 font-light leading-130 tracking-1"> <cite class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline not-italic text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd [&amp;&gt;a:hover]:text-gray-63 [&amp;&gt;a:hover]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;&gt;a:hover]:text-gray-bd dark:[&amp;&gt;a:hover]:shadow-underline-gray [&amp;&gt;a]:shadow-underline-gray-63 dark:[&amp;&gt;a]:text-gray-bd dark:[&amp;&gt;a]:shadow-underline-gray">Photo by Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge</cite></div></figure></div></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph my-12 font-fkroman text-17 leading-150 text-gray-13 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">The blood oxygen feature is about to disappear from new Apple Watch Series 9 and Watch Ultra 2 devices. While Apple itself has not released a statement or responded to our request for comment, both <em>Bloomberg</em> and <em>9to5Mac</em> are reporting that the feature will be going away and that US Customs and Border Protection has approved the measure, which would allow Apple to consider selling both products after their sale was banned last year.</p></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph my-12 font-fkroman text-17 leading-150 text-gray-13 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">The Apple Watch Series 9 and Watch Ultra 2 were both banned in the US late last year as the result of a patent dispute with medical device maker Masimo. The <a href="/2023/12/18/24006080/apple-watch-ban-series-9-ultra-2-itc-import">International Trade Commission (ITC) ruled</a> that the blood oxygen sensors in both devices infringed on patents from Masimo.</p></div><span class="mb-8 font-polysans text-15 font-medium leading-150 tracking-1 text-gray-13 "><a class="inline-block shadow-underline-black hover:shadow-highlight-franklin" href="/2024/1/15/24034324/apple-watch-ban-us-customs-decision">Read Article &gt;</a></span></div></div></div></li><li role="article" class="mx-[-16px] mb-40 mt-[-40px] px-16 last:mb-0 md:mx-0 md:px-0" id="stream-entry-22c5d732-6d15-415a-9068-5d55ce6eb3eb"><div class="border-solid border-blurple-df pt-40 sm:border-b-0 border-b"><div class="mb-40"><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card z-10 flex max-w-container-md flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col"><div class="mb-10 flex items-center"><div class="absolute left-[-2px] hidden h-6 w-12 border-y-2 border-white bg-[#DFCFFF] md:block"></div><div class="relative mr-8 block h-[36px] w-[36px] flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-solid border-gray-ef bg-[#DFCFFF]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="Jess Weatherbed" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="rounded-full" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="Jess Weatherbed" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover" class="rounded-full" sizes="36px" srcSet="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 16w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 32w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 48w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 64w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 96w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 128w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 256w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 376w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 384w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 415w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 480w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 540w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 640w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 750w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 828w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 1440w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg 2400w" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NMIz3MX90uIhy1IgwRMkzX0otTA=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195820/JESSICA_WEATHERBED.0.jpg"/></noscript></span></div><div class="font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-130 tracking-12 text-blurple"><p class="mb-2 font-bold">Jan 15</p><p><span><a class="hover:shadow-underline-blurple" href="/authors/jess-weatherbed">Jess Weatherbed</a></span></p></div></div><div class="font-polysans text-black dark:text-gray-ef leading-150"><div class="inline pr-4 text-17 font-bold md:text-17">Apple&#x27;s Watch workaround to avoid an import ban has reportedly been approved.</div><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10   [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:text-gray-33 [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-gray-33 dark:[&amp;_a]:text-gray-ef dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">Word of this comes not from US Customs, but Masimo’s own lawyers in a letter published by <a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/01/15/apple-watch-blood-oxygen-feature-remove-ban/"><em>9to5Mac</em></a>. It says the updated watches &quot;do not contain pulse oximetry functionality,&quot; which is a step further than last month&#39;s report that Apple engineers were <a href="/2023/12/18/24007277/apple-is-scrambling-on-software-changes-to-attempt-to-resolve-the-itcs-apple-watch-ban">working on new algorithms</a>. </p><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mt-12 font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10   [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:text-gray-33 [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-gray-33 dark:[&amp;_a]:text-gray-ef dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">It means Apple can continue importing the Apple Watch Series 9 and Apple Watch Ultra 2 <a href="/24009254/apple-watch-itc-ban-patent-dispute">despite the patent infringement dispute</a> — just without blood oxygen reading features enabled. </p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/01/15/apple-watch-blood-oxygen-feature-remove-ban/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Apple readies Apple Watch Series 9 ban workaround by disabling blood oxygen functionality</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->9to5Mac<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></li><li role="article" class="mx-[-16px] mb-40 mt-[-40px] px-16 last:mb-0 md:mx-0 md:px-0" id="stream-entry-ad96bc5f-9a49-40d7-ba30-8ece0a7c76e6"><div class="border-solid border-blurple-df pt-40 sm:border-b-0 border-b"><div class="mb-40"><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card z-10 flex max-w-container-md flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col"><div class="mb-10 flex items-center"><div class="absolute left-[-2px] hidden h-6 w-12 border-y-2 border-white bg-[#DFCFFF] md:block"></div><div class="relative mr-8 block h-[36px] w-[36px] flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-solid border-gray-ef bg-[#DFCFFF]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="Victoria Song" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="rounded-full" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="Victoria Song" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover" class="rounded-full" sizes="36px" srcSet="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 16w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 32w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 48w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 64w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 96w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 128w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 256w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 376w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 384w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 415w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 480w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 540w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 640w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 750w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 828w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 1440w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg 2400w" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BjR3J7Kmvpaurki5Tr96B2nQojM=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195849/VICTORIA_SONG.0.jpg"/></noscript></span></div><div class="font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-130 tracking-12 text-blurple"><p class="mb-2 font-bold">Jan 5</p><p><span><a class="hover:shadow-underline-blurple" href="/authors/victoria-song">Victoria Song</a></span></p></div></div><div class="font-polysans text-black dark:text-gray-ef leading-150"><div class="inline pr-4 text-17 font-bold md:text-17">Why the ITC denied staying the Apple Watch ban.</div><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10   [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:text-gray-33 [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-gray-33 dark:[&amp;_a]:text-gray-ef dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">The ITC’s opinion on the Apple Watch ban has been unsealed. You can read it at the link below, but there are no big surprises. The gist is the ITC didn’t think Apple proved it would suffer irreparable harm if the ban went through.</p><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mt-12 font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10   [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:text-gray-33 [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-gray-33 dark:[&amp;_a]:text-gray-ef dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">But the saga isn’t over yet. Shortly after the ban went into effect, a federal appeals court <a href="/2023/12/27/24016464/apple-watch-itc-ban-paused">issued a temporary pause</a>, meaning you <a href="/2023/12/27/24016684/apple-watch-on-sale-again-import-sales-bans-paused">can still buy the Series 9 and Ultra</a>. Right now, Apple’s waiting to hear back if proposed changes to the Apple Watch will render this patent beef moot. </p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24254209-itc-apple-opinion?responsive=1&amp;title=1" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">ITC Apple opinion</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->DocumentCloud<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></li><li role="article" class="mx-[-16px] mb-40 mt-[-40px] px-16 last:mb-0 md:mx-0 md:px-0" id="stream-entry-55c704b6-eebc-4dab-8b87-0d5a088618be"><div class="border-solid border-blurple-df pt-40 sm:border-b-0 border-b"><div class="mb-40"><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card z-10 flex max-w-container-md flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col"><div class="mb-10 flex items-center"><div class="absolute left-[-2px] hidden h-6 w-12 border-y-2 border-white bg-[#DFCFFF] md:block"></div><div class="relative mr-8 block h-[36px] w-[36px] flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-solid border-gray-ef bg-[#DFCFFF]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="Wes Davis" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="rounded-full" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="Wes Davis" loadin