le_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0380.jpg 2400w" src="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/2400x1600/filters:focal(1020x680:1021x681):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24933443/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0380.jpg"/></noscript></span><div class="duet--media--caption pt-6 font-polysans-mono text-12 font-light leading-130 tracking-1"> <cite class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline not-italic text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd [&amp;&gt;a:hover]:text-gray-63 [&amp;&gt;a:hover]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;&gt;a:hover]:text-gray-bd dark:[&amp;&gt;a:hover]:shadow-underline-gray [&amp;&gt;a]:shadow-underline-gray-63 dark:[&amp;&gt;a]:text-gray-bd dark:[&amp;&gt;a]:shadow-underline-gray">Photo by Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge</cite></div></figure></div></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph my-12 font-fkroman text-17 leading-150 text-gray-13 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">Apple has won a temporary pause of <a href="/2023/12/26/24012382/apple-import-ban-watch-series-9-ultra-2">the Apple Watch ban</a> that went into effect on Tuesday, so it will <a href="/2023/12/27/24016684/apple-watch-on-sale-again-import-sales-bans-paused">resume sales in Apple Stores starting today</a> (Wednesday) and on Apple.com by 3PM ET / 12PM ET tomorrow, December 28th. A federal appeals court ordered a halt on the import and sales bans today, after Apple requested that they be paused at least until US Customs can determine if changes it’s making to the Apple Watch would be enough to avoid the patent dispute that led to the ban. Customs is expected to issue its decision on January 12th.</p></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph my-12 font-fkroman text-17 leading-150 text-gray-13 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">The court’s order means that Apple can resume selling the Apple Watch Series 9 and Apple Watch Ultra 2 for the moment. Both watches were <a href="/2023/12/21/24010965/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-removed-from-online-sale-store">pulled from its website</a> last week and off of store shelves this week, as the ban went into effect. </p></div><span class="mb-8 font-polysans text-15 font-medium leading-150 tracking-1 text-gray-13 "><a class="inline-block shadow-underline-black hover:shadow-highlight-franklin" href="/2023/12/27/24016464/apple-watch-itc-ban-paused">Read Article &gt;</a></span></div></div></div></li><li role="article" class="mx-[-16px] mb-40 mt-[-40px] px-16 last:mb-0 md:mx-0 md:px-0" id="stream-entry-e6b2812e-09d8-4b82-95cd-5e877ab83294"><div class="border-solid border-blurple-df pt-40 sm:border-b-0 border-b"><div class="mb-40"><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card z-10 flex max-w-container-md flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col"><div class="mb-10 flex items-center"><div class="absolute left-[-2px] hidden h-6 w-12 border-y-2 border-white bg-[#DFCFFF] md:block"></div><div class="relative mr-8 block h-[36px] w-[36px] flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-solid border-gray-ef bg-[#DFCFFF]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="Richard Lawler" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="rounded-full" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="Richard Lawler" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover" class="rounded-full" sizes="36px" srcSet="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 16w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 32w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 48w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 64w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 96w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 128w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 256w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 376w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 384w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 415w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 480w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 540w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 640w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 750w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 828w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 1440w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg 2400w" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wrKOBdPIqNcsmXvexHJDy5bcrJg=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195843/RICHARD_LAWLER.0.jpg"/></noscript></span></div><div class="font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-130 tracking-12 text-blurple"><p class="mb-2 font-bold">Dec 27, 2023</p><p><span><a class="hover:shadow-underline-blurple" href="/authors/richard-lawler">Richard Lawler</a></span></p></div></div><div class="font-polysans text-black dark:text-gray-ef leading-150"><div class="inline pr-4 text-17 font-bold md:text-17">Meet Marcelo Lamego, a key figure in the patent battle that’s banned Apple watches.</div><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10   [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:text-gray-33 [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-gray-33 dark:[&amp;_a]:text-gray-ef dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin"><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/what-started-the-apple-watch-ban-saga-a-late-night-email-to-ceo-tim-cook"><em>Bloomberg</em></a> reporter Mark Gurman goes into the history of Masimo’s patent infringement <a href="/24009254/apple-watch-itc-ban-patent-dispute">case against Apple’s wearables</a>, explaining that Lamego was the CTO at a Masimo spinoff. He rebuffed one inquiry from Apple, but in 2013 he emailed Apple CEO Tim Cook at 1AM about working there and joined a few months later:</p><blockquote class="duet--article--blockquote jzbdts3 jzbdts2"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup jzbdtsi jzbdtsa jzbdts0">Lawyers for Masimo say that Lamego lacked prior knowledge about how to develop the blood-oxygen feature (his previous studies were about neural interfaces rather than health sensors). He learned how to build the technology at Kiani’s companies and delivered it to Apple, they say.</p><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup jzbdtsi jzbdtsa jzbdts0">Lamego then resigned from Apple in July 2014, just months after joining. Masimo argues that he left after Apple got what it needed.</p></blockquote><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mt-12 font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10   [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:text-gray-33 [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-gray-33 dark:[&amp;_a]:text-gray-ef dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">Masimo also says Apple hired its former chief medical officer and 20 or so other staffers, while Apple claims he wasn’t a good fit.</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/what-started-the-apple-watch-ban-saga-a-late-night-email-to-ceo-tim-cook" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">What Started the Apple Watch Ban Saga? A Late-Night Email to CEO Tim Cook</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->Bloomberg<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></li><li role="article" class="mx-[-16px] mb-40 mt-[-40px] px-16 last:mb-0 md:mx-0 md:px-0" id="stream-entry-61ef34fb-47a7-46a2-ae6b-1c0fe3f231ee"><div class="border-solid border-blurple-df pt-40 sm:border-b-0 border-b"><div class="mb-40"><div><div class="mb-10 flex items-center"><div class="absolute left-[-2px] hidden h-6 w-12 border-y-2 border-white bg-[#DFCFFF] md:block"></div><div class="relative mr-8 block h-[36px] w-[36px] flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-solid border-gray-ef bg-[#DFCFFF]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="Ariel Shapiro" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="rounded-full" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="Ariel Shapiro" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="po