d our original story about the appeal below. </em></p></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph my-12 font-fkroman text-17 leading-150 text-gray-13 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">Apple has filed an appeal to the International Trade Commission’s decision to ban U.S. sales of Watch Series 9 and Watch Ultra 2 models, <a href="https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24238097-apple-watch-masimo-itc-appeal?responsive=1&title=1">court records</a> show. Additionally, the company is requesting an emergency stay on the ban for at least two weeks until a decision is made on redesigned versions of the banned models.</p></div><span class="mb-8 font-polysans text-15 font-medium leading-150 tracking-1 text-gray-13 "><a class="inline-block shadow-underline-black hover:shadow-highlight-franklin" href="/2023/12/26/24015238/apple-watch-ban-response-store-appeal-stay-court">Read Article &gt;</a></span></div></div></div></li><li role="article" class="mx-[-16px] mb-40 mt-[-40px] px-16 last:mb-0 md:mx-0 md:px-0" id="stream-entry-c613f844-110d-4fa2-89f5-a8513502a563"><div class="border-solid border-blurple-df pt-40 sm:border-b-0 border-b"><div class="mb-40"><div><div class="mb-10 flex items-center"><div class="absolute left-[-2px] hidden h-6 w-12 border-y-2 border-white bg-[#DFCFFF] md:block"></div><div class="relative mr-8 block h-[36px] w-[36px] flex-none overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-solid border-gray-ef bg-[#DFCFFF]"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="Emma Roth" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="rounded-full" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="Emma Roth" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover" class="rounded-full" sizes="36px" srcSet="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 16w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 32w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 48w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 64w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 96w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 128w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 256w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 376w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0.jpg 384w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/827LG_ByqUcThMiE8B1E8Gx5gPY=/512x512/cdn.vox-cdn.com/author_profile_images/195810/EMMA_ROTH.0